25.1
* Merged all sub projects into lcarsde
* Rewrite app selector, menu and logout in Kotlin (JVM based); breaking change for status-bar configuration
* Remove launcher.py and launch apps using dex (new dependency)
* Remove all Python dependencies
* As a result of the package merge, all parts of lcarsde are now licensed under GNU GPL V2 from this version on
* New status bar LcarsdeStatusAudio widget -> breaking changes in configuration
    * Old audio widget properties are gone
    * New properties added: volumeIncrease, volumeDecrease with integer percent values as steps for increasing/decreasing audio volume
* IMPORTANT: Check files in /etc/lcarsde/ and /etc/xdg/autostart/. Remove old files and adjust the installed files. Remove the .dpkg-new file name ending if necessary.
